Adapun salah satu hal yang perlu dilakukan dalam ajang ini adalah memberikan pandangan terkait globalisasi dan bagaimana menghadapinya sehingga ke-Indonesia-an dapat dipertahankan. 
Inilah sedikit pemikiran saya mengenai hal tersebut.

caption.text:
[CHRONICS 2017 CALL FOR PARTICIPANTS]

Greetings, creative minds!

As we know, the crime rate in Asia is getting higher every year. Regardless of where you live, work or play, you can become a victim since crime doesn't play favorites. Robbery, burglary, aggravated assaults, armed or otherwise, can happen to anyone, anywhere. And it could be you, looking at danger in the eye.

My name is Andre Jason and I'm pleased to invite you to join CHRONICS 2017 with this year's theme "Innovative Breakthroughs in Crime Prevention". This year will be the tenth time CHRONICS gathers outstanding undergraduates from all around Southeast Asia to compete and exhibit their unique and astonishing products here in Yogyakarta, Indonesia. Come join us and let's be a part of the solution to make the world a better place!

Still think you're a brilliant designer? We challenge you, for real.

REGISTER NOW! 
Head straight to our official website www.chronics.ft.ugm.ac.id for more info.

Be an opponent, not a victim.

Find us on our social media!
